//circle.hydla
//bouncing particle in a circle

INIT   <=> 0 < x < 3/4 /\ y=0 /\ vx=2 /\ vy=1 /\ [](x' = vx /\ y' = vy).
RUN    <=> [](vx'=0 /\ vy'=0).
BOUNCE <=> []((x-)^2+(y-)^2=1 => 
                vx = vx- - (x-*vx- + y-*vy-)*(1+1)*(x-) /\
                vy = vy- - (x-*vx- + y-*vy-)*(1+1)*(y-)
).
INIT, RUN<<BOUNCE.
